    "text": "Users' home directories/folders may contain\n                        information of a sensitive nature. Non-privileged users should coordinate\n                        any sharing of information with an SA through shared resources. <html:pre xmlns:html=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n                        Script Verification:\n                            To manually verify, run command 'cat /etc/shadow and verify that no\n                        additional users exist\n                        </html:pre>\n                    ",
